Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.79,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I thought, there's no way that running...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.88,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And getting married would work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.44,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.18,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to dream that it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:09.93,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I felt like if I hadn't done something right then, everything would fall apart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.41,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both you and Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing's fallen apart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.46,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can just start from here instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:24.98,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't have to run away to get married, we can do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.80,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's better to get everyone's blessing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.11,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Everyone" as in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.02,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandpa, Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.27,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.97,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That might take some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.34,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:47.96,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to be happy anyway, why not be happy with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.61,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.62,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.16,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's try it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.14,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:03.96,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.63,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I, Takasu Ryuuji, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.03,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.44,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever, just make something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.84,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't just make up whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.19,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will take Aisaka Taiga as my wife—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.25,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevermind, I don't need a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.17,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.77,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the one that said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.47,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you remember what you said a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.91,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said, "We're the tiger and dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.87,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Since a long time ago, we've always been thought of as equals."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:46.67,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why we'll always be by each other's side, without any kind of promises, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:50.94,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.78,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your eyes are bloodshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.26,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're breathing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.36,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.65,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your lips are peeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.29,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It looks like it'd hurt if we kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.50,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like we're ever going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.28,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.23,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.41,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'd hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.17,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.17,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just as I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.04,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was really rough, like a starving barren wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.49,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.92,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.05,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, it's cold, so one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.34,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.95,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.20,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somehow... {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.15,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.20,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Going, it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.32,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But coming home, it's three people plus one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.57,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, you were confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That Yacchan would come flying if we told a lie like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.98,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then make up with Grandma and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.31,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like I was confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't think it would absolutely be okay, but I didn't think it would definitely be bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.36,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe that's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:39.62,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe that's just how a family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.92,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.37,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.87,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're eating dinner at our place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.80,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.59,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.26,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're a family of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.39,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.89,TD_Main,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}I-In...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.08,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}I forgot about you, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:00.88,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.08,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.44,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to change my clothes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But your parents will be in your apartment—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.33,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.35,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.62,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.38,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tonight's your favorite, pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.05,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.55,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, what are you think—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.43,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really understand what's going to hap—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.36,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quit foo—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.55,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.30,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.35,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really hate me that mu—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.13,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.64,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care what you do or where you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.18,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going home, so do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.41,TD_Main,Mama,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.02,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with that? She's a kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.37,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:33.19,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always, always thought that someone like me would never be loved by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.61,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.78,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not just pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.71,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma taught me how to make some great meat stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.53,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.04,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.65,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...but maybe that was just me running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't see any stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.72,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.52,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's awkward and unreliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:00.80,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:07.52,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I blamed my lack of confidence on my parents and everyone around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:12.16,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you love me just as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.06,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.40,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.59,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will accept everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:27.74,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I want to love you with my head held high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.00,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That night, Taiga didn't come over for the pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.17,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.43,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We won't get it if you don't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.88,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.49,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did Taiga—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.14,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, everyone, get in your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.85,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have some bad news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:54.15,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san is withdrawing for family reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:12:00.19,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've just heard from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.49,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san will be going back to her mother's—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.11,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.32,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a lie, right? It's a complete lie, right? They made her, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.65,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She didn't tell us any—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.78,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From here on out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:12.37,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will all come to a lot of different crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.00,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whether you want to stop there or turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:19.86,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will have to choose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.01,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san's choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.93,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}May lead to leaving all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:30.22,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'm sure it's a choice she thought very hard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.52,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:32.63,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.76,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How scary kids these days are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.21,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're all calling Aisaka-san at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.01,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Texting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:41.82,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.85,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about a little more time to reflect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.07,TD_2nd,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.13,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't connect if we all call at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.12,TD_2nd,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, get in your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:53.46,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.03,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushie—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.67,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait. {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.05,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could you grit your teeth for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.68,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why were you the only one who came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.46,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is Taiga transferring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:08.98,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.93,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Takas—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.61,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.57,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.80,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.29,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't want to let her go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:18.89,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.19,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I could, I would drag her back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.75,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why'd you decide on everything by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.27,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.95,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:34.45,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.83,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only thing I can do now is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.46,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:55.14,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now she decides to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.15,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.48,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A sock without its pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.47,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.15,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.70,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll definitely find him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.28,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait... {jama: added}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.79,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't this stuff she was supposed to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.10,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really a dummy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.93,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.28,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I fell into the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.62,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.23,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the middle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.69,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I even said it to Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.58,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.90,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really dumb too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.35,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomiya-kun, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.14,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's somewhere I want to go on the way home, can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.59,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.31,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.43,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.24,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I'm sorry for yesterday."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.75,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is what I'm not thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.33,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're not thinking it, then don't bother telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:52.78,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I think I get what you said, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.06,TD_Main,GIrl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey, Taiga's text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.86,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It came, it came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.72,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.97,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.99,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.84,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like it came to everyone who texted Taiga yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.28,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But why is it just a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.90,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.06,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, what is it actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:11.41,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.78,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.26,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:15.85,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.41,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that small shining thing a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.77,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.06,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.92,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's definitely a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.13,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But why the night sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.06,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I will be watching over you all from a far-off sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.22,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's bad luck! She's not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.26,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I'm going to try hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.05,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think is what she's trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.57,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even in a sky that is so dark you can't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:42.56,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will definitely be stars somewhere there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.40,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.44,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I shine even more brightly than I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.98,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure people will be able to see me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.24,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she's being...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.94,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretty selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.62,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:00.51,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sky is all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.26,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as each of us can shine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.37,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No matter how far apart we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:10.04,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can see how each other is trying really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.25,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was so badly done, I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.42,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chills went down my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.55,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.61,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I kind of like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.27,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Feels like youth, don'cha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.21,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.65,TD_Main,Kihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like it if she was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.21,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.48,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone at some time had a lot of trouble with a certain star once...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.12,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.59,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she'd be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:39.07,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we replied to her picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.16,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.58,TD_Main,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.57,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did we put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:49.04,TD_Main,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I remember putting it away afterwards with Ami-chan's tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.25,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:58.66,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thinking of ways to make other people happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.75,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.05,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.17,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.18,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After all, my existence itself is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.09,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know, I used to think Taiga was exactly as she seemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:16.22,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Running head-strong into everyone, but even so, loved as she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.02,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:18.57,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.84,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:26.36,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though she has a big attitude, her heart is as cowardly as her small body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.63,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though she's always trying to figure out what everyone's thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.67,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She won't ever let anyone see her real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's just the same as a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.15,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.01,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She was seen through by a certain someone from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:42.34,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said I was a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:45.77,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate the me that pretends to be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:49.83,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I was anxious to have others accept me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.90,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But watching Taiga, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.53,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As long as there's one person who understands me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.50,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:18:59.81,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.02,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.15,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.16,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Treasure ahoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.45,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just have to press here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.58,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:18.17,TD_Main,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please hurry up while I still have my god powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.86,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, Takasu-kun, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.00,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:26.85,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:27.96,TD_Main,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.23,TD_Main,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.19,TD_Main,Sensei,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.85,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.65,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:46.29,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since a long time ago, tigers and dragons have stood together as equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:46.95,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.75,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're not here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.77,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're always by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.21,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Transcending time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.05,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.17,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.01,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.86,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this color a bit too flashy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.56,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yacchan's a mother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.30,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe I should use a nude lip gloss or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.41,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I don't have anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.35,TD_Main,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.98,TD_Main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-Inko-chan said his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.68,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be lonely once the third years leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.05,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There were a lot of really interesting people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.05,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:16.79,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The student council president, Kitamura-senpai, will be studying in America after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:22.39,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cultural and sports festival were amazing when he and the third years organized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.63,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:27.03,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I heard that the cultural festival from the year before was even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:28.56,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, I heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.72,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one where the legendary class, 2-C, won everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.79,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:35.10,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something about how somebody by the name of Tenori something had a huge role...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.02,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tenori something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.73,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean Tenori Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.96,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one who brings you happiness, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.36,TD_Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was a real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.80,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, yeah, Tenori Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.80,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Apparently she was at this school last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.53,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.82,TD_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's Takasu-senpai's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:02.67,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's something that not a single person in this world has seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.38,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's gentle, and very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.84,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probably, if they ever had the chance to see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.54,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyone would want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.51,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.52,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one has ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.35,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why the world hid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.40,TD_Thoughts,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that you couldn't get it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:21.91,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:23.98,TD_Thoughts,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday someone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.93,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That one person who should have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:42.55,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will be able to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.88,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:48.92,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was going to scare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.17,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:55.21,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I haven't shrunk nor grown a single millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:56.77,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So sorry to disappoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.14,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:22:59.92,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:07.44,TD_Main,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:12.27,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why are you saying something so embarrassing in broad daylight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:15.25,TD_Main,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Things like that n-need a certain mood or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.24,TD_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's how it's made.
